{"tid":896401,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好唔捨得你","createTime":"2018-11-10T04:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T11:46:43.000Z","uid":120825,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"db68512f9704ddf549fbfad746c40db2243dee65","tid":896401,"uid":120825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:03:08.000Z","msg":"係大學認識你，展開我的初戀。<br />\n<br />\n我地asso yr1 sem b 相識一齊努力讀書，兩年後大家都升到大學，但分開左讀兩間大學。兩年後大家都出黎社會做野。<br />\n<br />\n岩岩開始拍拖既時候，我知道係你愛我多過我愛你，但慢慢一齊耐左，我愈來愈鐘意你。雖然你唔係一個靚女，一開始仲因為同你一齊而比朋友笑，但我都唔知點解會慢慢愛上你，讓我欣賞你既優點包容你既缺點，可能就真係因爲愛。<br />\n<br />\n到今日，你想分開冷靜下，但我好掛住你，又唔可以搵你怕煩到你。<br />\n<br />\n我知道自己唔夠浪漫，又唔夠細心，又比唔到驚喜你。<br />\n<br />\n但我真係好鐘意你，好唔捨得你。<br />\n<br />\n點解愛情咁脆弱，點解你可以咁絕情...<br />\n<br />\n原來失戀係咁辛苦。"},{"pid":"b64e9668026a73e6806b7a2ba29c607d3a7cefd4","tid":896401,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:06:22.000Z","msg":"珍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654d3cdfe65249be281d33101736dc0fb2b1b02c","tid":896401,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:43:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8b4998606dc3bb347fde922ee4cbc7f520c8f0","tid":896401,"uid":78595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:00:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e723e2fd29000ac2319d943df21eca89440d6c6b","tid":896401,"uid":220228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:30:53.000Z","msg":"ching加油"},{"pid":"79e275d4d03836b8e55bf9c19ea67624dced22e1","tid":896401,"uid":120825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e723e2fd29000ac231